Kenya Reinsurance to Establish Shariah-Compliant Unit, Business Daily Says

-- B y   E r i c   O m b o k
-- 
2011-06-13T04:09:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-13/kenya-reinsurance-to-establish-shariah-compliant-unit-business-daily-says.html
Kenya Reinsurance Corp. plans to
establish a Shariah-compliant unit as it seeks grow its income
by tapping into the expanding Islamic-finance industry in  Africa 
and the Middle East, Business Daily reported.  Kenya Re, as the state-run reinsurer is known, will
additionally venture into micro-insurance and political-risk
insurance, the Nairobi-based newspaper said, citing Chief
Executive Officer Jadiah Mwarania.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eric Ombok in Nairobi at 
 eombok@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  